    "text": "Previous reports related yield promoting effects to the region harboring the flowering locus eps2 (barley HvCEN gene). Sequencing of a 1025 bp fragment encompassing the HvCEN coding region revealed no Single Nucleotide Polymorphism (SNP) variation in our parents and near-isogenic lines, ruling out direct involvement of eps2. These findings pointed to another flowering locus in the QTL region.",
